rComments: Amazing prof, best class I have ever had

Amazing Prof. He explains things well and constantly checks to make sure everyone is understanding. Very organized and systematic teaching style. (His notes are amazing). He's also super nice, and approachable if you ever have questions. Also, tutorials are very recommended, the TA, reviews the whole weeks worth of work in one hour.

I had him for my Calculus and Numerical Methods Course. He was excellent and teaches with enthusiasm. His exams are really application based, sometimes tough but his grading scheme is very good. He cares for his students. The best part is he never takes more than 1 hour to respond to your email, extremely approachable.

First time teaching this course. It is challenging and he could be a bit clearer in lecture, but he always asks for feedback and goes over material when people tell him they are lost. Helpful guy, heart in the right place!
